nodes.text: Avrac Kefundee was a criminal who was serving a 25-year sentence in the Wobani Penitentiary for aggravated assault of a New Republic officer. Kefundee's profile in the New Republic prison registry was one of several that Marshal Carasynthia Dune looked at from her office on the planet Nevarro in around 9 ABY while searching for the profile of prisoner Migs Mayfeld.
Avrac Kefundee's profile first appeared in "Chapter 14: The Tragedy", the sixth episode of the second season of The Mandalorian, which was released on December 4, 2020.
